tm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42ab=
d12a ), Zelensky=E2=80=99s ambassador to Washington, Oksana Markarova, appa=
rently offered to resign and take the bullet for the misstep. But Zelensky =
refused. Instead, she lived long enough in the position to
become infamous, as Kremlin TV put it ( https://smotrim.ru/brand/5206?utm_c=
ampaign=3DThe+Best+%26+The+Brightest+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%283%2F3%2F25%29&utm_con=
