yUyODMlMkYzJTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fY29udGVudD1UaGUrQmVzdCslMjYrVGhlK0JyaWdo=
dGVzdCstK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODMlMkYzJTJGMjUlMjlcdTAwMjZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWl=
sX2FjdGlvblx1MDAyNnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9Y3VzdG9tZXIuaW9cdTAwMjZ1dG1fdGVybT1mNmM2MD=
YxN2RhNDJhYmQxMmEiLCJpbnRlcm5hbCI6ImY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImxpbmtfaWQiO=
jIxMDMxNzd9/aa4660b706a39e5d4bd1358384f6a259e4afff38d5ddcc23af29c41940c2fce=
b" style=3D"text-decoration:underline;color:#d40000;">previous
reporting</a> that =E2=80=9Cthis was not planned in advance or part of a br=
oader strategy, but simply just how the day played out.=E2=80=9D) Another M=
oscow source, who is under U.S. indictment, echoed that sentiment, telling =
me that he had =E2=80=9Ctalked to the administration before and after [the =
meeting], and I don=E2=80=99t think anyone expected it to go that way or th=
at Zelensky would behave that way.=E2=80=9D<br/><br/>For what it=E2=80=99s =
worth, I agree. If you=E2=80=99re going into the dragon=E2=80=99s den of yo=
ur own volition, be prepared for the
dragon to spit fire at you, and, you know, be a dragon. Zelensky knew exact=
ly how the president and vice president felt about him and his country vers=
us how they felt about Russia and <strong>Vladimir Putin</strong>. He arriv=
ed clearly keyed up after weeks of Trump praising Putin, calling Zelensky a=
 dictator and trying to extort Ukraine. It didn=E2=80=99t help that, as soo=
n as the Ukrainian president descended from his black SUV, Trump tweaked hi=
m on the White House steps and in front of the cameras
about not wearing a suit. <br/><br/>The suit obsession is so stupid, but Kr=
emlin propaganda has been <a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF=
9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lEQUt2UktxclJLZ0dWWHBDOHFiVlNDampOUVVETlcwTT0iLCJocmVmIjoia=
HR0cHM6Ly9zbW90cmltLnJ1L2JyYW5kLzUyMDY_dXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPVRoZStCZXN0KyUyNitU=
aGUrQnJpZ2h0ZXN0Ky0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MyUyRjMlMkYyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb25=
0ZW50PVRoZStCZXN0KyUyNitUaGUrQnJpZ2h0ZXN0Ky0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MyUyRjMlMk=
YyNSUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWxfYWN0aW9uXHUwMDI2dXRtX3NvdXJjZT1jdXN0b=
21lci5pb1x1MDAyNnV0bV90ZXJtPWY2YzYwNjE3ZGE0MmFiZDEyYSIsImludGVybmFsIjoiZjZj=
NjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMTJhIiwibGlua19pZCI6NTQwMzc1fQ/aacbc69b35e65b5ff36cebeecffb=
a6a1a395b524da05d2a9313b68e8a5d21554" style=3D"text-decoration:underline;co=
lor:#d40000;">engaging</a> in some hardcore anthropology, extensively analy=
zing the supposed White House dress code and explaining what they see as an=
 elaborate American etiquette around clothing. (Of course, they omitted tha=
t this supposed dress code in no way applies to First Buddy <strong>Elon</s=
trong>.) Still, this is
what Zelensky signed up for just by asking for the meeting. And that, even =
his supporters here say, was his first mistake.</p></div>
