line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;">What=E2=80=99s more, Trump was quiet and deferential in the first=
 part of the spray, which
Zelensky unwisely used to launch into a presentation of sorts. He immediate=
ly started listing the equipment and weapons he wanted, showed Trump photos=
 of Ukrainian P.O.W.s on their return from Russian captivity, and couldn=E2=
=80=99t stop after one or two or even three. It was like watching someone w=
ho had been so nervous for the meeting that they stayed up all night crammi=
ng, only for everything to come out in one confused, pressurized stream. <b=
r/><br/>The issue, of course, is that Zelensky wasn=E2=80=99t just
some novice fumbling a PowerPoint presentation. He is now a seasoned wartim=
e leader on whom tens of millions of lives=E2=80=94and Ukraine=E2=80=99s ve=
ry sovereignty=E2=80=94depend. He has addressed seemingly every important r=
